{"tid":1964310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我今日真係覺得好攰好無力","createTime":"2020-04-08T17:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T03:56:27.000Z","uid":99069,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"96005c157e4f092512d653b5703fd5ae542cc80f","tid":1964310,"uid":99069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:21:05.000Z","msg":"今日見到金大仙channel share返一個上年嘅post<br />\n<br />\n我今年中六 等緊上庭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1678699\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1678699</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇完篇文之後 我真係喊到收唔到聲<br />\n<br />\n出返去熱門 望住唔少post都同運動無關<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/004433_05ee5ab3e45f5a4b4c4b3468be3455b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F004433_05ee5ab3e45f5a4b4c4b3468be3455b5.jpg&h=d3722f52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/004446_ccbfe59ee334e084714e462ad0ed2a7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F004446_ccbfe59ee334e084714e462ad0ed2a7c.jpg&h=4cf96047&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/broAT4C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbroAT4C.jpg&h=cb957127&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/004409_ee6bcaf86fa97ed86c661c811d4a0312.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F004409_ee6bcaf86fa97ed86c661c811d4a0312.jpg&h=a551c4e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CM9gDv4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCM9gDv4.jpg&h=77c7580b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（post完相排序唔同咗）<br />\n<br />\n嗰下真係好攰好無力<br />\n唔係話要大家每日都唔開心<br />\n唔可以係連登到開同運動無關嘅post<br />\n但連仔專登出咗<span style=\"color: red;\">不推文模式</span><br />\n大家可以更加善用<br />\n明白出post嘅各位<br />\n都會好想自己嘅post多啲人睇到<br />\n但光復香港 唔係更重要咩？<br />\n求下各位 幫手推下行動post建議post<br />\n可唔可以返翻去上年嘅6789月<br />\n熱門全部post都係行動post<br />\n有行動嘅日子連登會比人ddos<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記我哋嘅手足<br />\n如果唔係有佢地 我哋今日已經通過咗送中<br />\n我哋未來嘅小朋友 <br />\n可能就會同你講習爺爺手好溫暖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">運動post傳送門</span></span><br />\n<br />\n疫情過後，全球局勢大洗牌，國際戰線為重要<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1963956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1963956</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【本土思潮】你有可能已經俾中共洗咗腦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1963919\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1963919</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想打國際線嘅<br />\nTG bot <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbqC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=cb70e1f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n明白大家平時可能做野忙 <br />\n但返工放工都要出街 如果見到狗車 <br />\n儘量報哨好唔好？<br />\n以前係街到見有狗車 仲打緊字報哨嘅時候 <br />\n已經見有channel post咗出嚟<br />\n但到而家 見到channel都開始慢慢靜咗落嚟 <br />\n我就知道 大家少咗報哨<br />\n應承我 <span style=\"color: red;\">全民報哨</span>好唔好？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/011048_cb2e1b1bea9a3be579a2a748f8b1c829.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F011048_cb2e1b1bea9a3be579a2a748f8b1c829.jpg&h=69425daa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 唔只係一句口號<br />\n時代革命 我哋係被選中嘅一代<br />\n我哋有能力做更多野 捍衛我哋嘅自由<br />\n法治已死 所以我哋更加要打倒呢個不公嘅政權<br />\n記住我哋 五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n呢排出唔到街 我哋留係屋企打國際線<br />\n盡我哋所能 捍衛我哋嘅香港"},{"pid":"224effed426ed5c53a97d9bf0fac74aa33c693aa","tid":1964310,"uid":99069,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:21:50.000Z","msg":"有錯屌細力少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d0921c9419003a203615631daf58a7becf6682","tid":1964310,"uid":99069,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/012232_58b83e137cf0e90e6a430a701cdeedbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F012232_58b83e137cf0e90e6a430a701cdeedbd.jpg&h=88926d13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/012244_ab78483a7a6908c9e922eb9acd9993a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F012244_ab78483a7a6908c9e922eb9acd9993a7.jpg&h=f70d4965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/012257_86e5287aa4d91bd498c36e8c18a2e42e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F012257_86e5287aa4d91bd498c36e8c18a2e42e.jpg&h=0499380a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cAHxWvG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcAHxWvG.jpg&h=4cbec826&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"189eebf32a6117fceaa31ccd0e61226d9fa2202b","tid":1964310,"uid":99069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:24:49.000Z","msg":"以上以下圖片都由TG channel 搵出嚟<br />\n<br />\n⚠️反送中 文宣谷 Channel⚠️<br />\n🔥【重要連結】🔥<br />\n請協助分享～🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n《頻道》<br />\n中文: @hkstandstrong_promo<br />\n國際: @hkstandstrong_promo_int"},{"pid":"2c9e65cf5e42c30f455ef4354deee53a98efa583","tid":1964310,"uid":99069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:25:36.000Z","msg":"推到有人入嚟睇"},{"pid":"ddcabbae28f8886e17ccfd24106eb4aeb0020faa","tid":1964310,"uid":314673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:25:53.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be50f9d65f1ee1f9a7ef664f5855476445ff8bda","tid":1964310,"uid":99069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T17:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/012608_0ed9a23417e5ed16128c6cc56217abe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F012608_0ed9a23417e5ed16128c6cc56217abe4.jpg&h=f52f49c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXkoiK2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXkoiK2.jpg&h=58e6f59b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/012617_ba26a73f585e2d6cdefe8b2a44220a62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F012617_ba26a73f585e2d6cdefe8b2a44220a62.jpg&h=e86fdfbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P94TFYq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP94TFYq.jpg&h=00be2a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/012627_3d5dd6c6a0100173d470ad41930c42b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F012627_3d5dd6c6a0100173d470ad41930c42b1.jpg&h=b1dcd797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VnjsLp9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVnjsLp9.jpg&h=35603e2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/09/012638_4ec152fd7f217b19ceed7d20a4fea5bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F012638_4ec152fd7f217b19ceed7d20a4fea5bb.jpg&h=3002935d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adb6e0019d46ed85066f445fa94aa307319daabf","tid":1964310,"uid":99069,"like":0,"d